  "title": "🦅 Client & Talent Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br />Kickstart your career with Euphoria Organization as a Client & Talent Executive! 🌟 You’ll be the driving force behind sales and recruitment, connecting with clients, attracting top talent, and making an impact in a vibrant, growth-focused environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Drive sales and achieve monthly targets 💼</p></li><li><p>Recruit, interview, and onboard talented candidates</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong client and candidate relationships</p></li><li><p>Contribute ideas for campaigns and engagement strategies 💡</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Fresh graduates or early career starters</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Energetic, proactive, and team-oriented</p></li></ul><p><strong>Perks:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Mentorship and career development programs</p></li><li><p>Fun team events 🎉</p></li><li><p>Opportunity for rapid growth in a supportive environment</p></li></ul>",
